d 先知道y price 升/跌/不變<br />\n如果demand 不變, y price 就increases"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"我代入啲例子 就諗唔到 <br />\n我用豬肉同豬肝<br />\n豬肉supply 跌會令到 豬肝supply 跌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"即係豬肝supply跌暗示豬嘅supply跌 所以豬肉同豬肝supply都會跌 應該係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"但咁咪變成good z 嘅supply跌導致good x and y嘅suppl跌？<br />\n同題目嘅good x導致good y好似唔同？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fee3df58ce303d1537e479d29ecd68907460ac7","tid":2263694,"uid":160229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d7d66a4f58858163a11e180ea9cff2cd772820d","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2501d5c4a69c4a9416b1d52d72af7865a5c4c429","tid":2263694,"uid":160229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1b02cf0491c3a93d46a03e71c974ed665fc93a0","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"我代入啲例子 就諗唔到 <br />\n我用豬肉同豬肝<br />\n豬肉supply 跌會令到 豬肝supply 跌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"即係豬肝supply跌暗示豬嘅supply跌 所以豬肉同豬肝supply都會跌 應該係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"但咁咪變成good z 嘅supply跌導致good x and y嘅suppl跌？<br />\n同題目嘅good x導致good y好似唔同？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"joint supply唔代表good x導致good y嘛？"},{"pid":"489f8103e238d98914505c768e126f94aa5f1cc9","tid":2263694,"uid":23445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d1b02cf0491c3a93d46a03e71c974ed665fc93a0","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d617f3ad648decb1d1dbc9c507a5c56589bb60","tid":2263694,"uid":23445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"Good y supply decreases, <br />\n要睇埋demand 先知道y price 升/跌/不變<br />\n如果demand 不變, y price 就increases"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"我代入啲例子 就諗唔到 <br />\n我用豬肉同豬肝<br />\n豬肉supply 跌會令到 豬肝supply 跌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"Joint supply 即係一件product 有兩個output: x, y <br />\n例如: <br />\n豬 -&gt; 豬肉, 豬內臟<br />\n牛 -&gt; 牛肉, 牛皮<br />\n<br />\n豬肉減少, 亦都代表豬內臟減少"},{"pid":"82b994032879da350b558192ac8f94bfd729e886","tid":2263694,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bc156efb6f1b138184a4d35f3dc745831dffa54","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"已知good x and good y are joint supply，如果good x supply decreases，good y嘅price會點變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"Increase <br />\n因為當豬肉=good x<br />\n豬皮=good Y<br />\nSupply decrease=price increase,quantity increase<br />\nGood X supply decrease連帶 good Y supply decrease <br />\nThen,good y price increase"},{"pid":"0f8f8f05aaa5164ca559cd46ac31116944b220e5","tid":2263694,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82b994032879da350b558192ac8f94bfd729e886","tid":2263694,"uid":185696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bc156efb6f1b138184a4d35f3dc745831dffa54","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"已知good x and good y are joint supply，如果good x supply decreases，good y嘅price會點變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"Increase <br />\n因為當豬肉=good x<br />\n豬皮=good Y<br />\nSupply decrease=price increase,quantity increase<br />\nGood X supply decrease連帶 good Y supply decrease <br />\nThen,good y price increase"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"Quantity decrease*"},{"pid":"3e41dc3e043b6a8d7536e3d366004a98365c5676","tid":2263694,"uid":236099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"Good x及good y係joint supply (這是前題)<br />\n唔洗諗「豬肉供應少左就豬肝供應一定會少左」是否在現實成立，呢個係前題<br />\n<br />\n總之佢係joint supply就= good x supply decreases, good y supply also decreases<br />\n<br />\n之後你要另一個假設，兩者需求不變<br />\n咁就會知兩者價錢上升<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩估，十年前alevel econ A"},{"pid":"bc0643a632ab461d77826211a365288071226286","tid":2263694,"uid":236099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1b02cf0491c3a93d46a03e71c974ed665fc93a0","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d617f3ad648decb1d1dbc9c507a5c56589bb60","tid":2263694,"uid":23445,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"Good y supply decreases, <br />\n要睇埋demand 先知道y price 升/跌/不變<br />\n如果demand 不變, y price 就increases"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"我代入啲例子 就諗唔到 <br />\n我用豬肉同豬肝<br />\n豬肉supply 跌會令到 豬肝supply 跌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"考試黎講 你唔應該去搞人地個「joint supply」前題<br />\n豬肉supply decreases, 豬肝supply will also decrease係人地個前題，你就照用<br />\n<br />\n你係都要諗現實生活成唔成立，你就實諗到exceptions<br />\n例如: 明天政府限制豬肝出口，但唔限制一般豬肉出口，咁個assumption咪唔成立囉<br />\n咁你個analysis咪唔applicable囉，但唔代表個analysis係錯"},{"pid":"8d879232c40be32dee73bb10785484c987391b92","tid":2263694,"uid":161603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:44:26.000Z","msg":"正統嚟講，用Qs去理解最好<br />\n<br />\nX supply decrease; Qs decrease<br />\nThus,<br />\nY supply also decrease, price increase<br />\n<br />\n同樣問題，轉做Price of X decrease , 你又可以諗下"},{"pid":"aded44d1e25cf10f8b8a9aa7c0dffeacbc102642","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"其實唔只supply，有時demand都會有類似的問題。<br />\n例如政府立法提高對盜版軟件的買家的懲罰，對盜版軟件的需求會下降，盜版軟件的均衡價格會下降。咁正版軟件的需求會如何改變？"},{"pid":"daf472514cf77c14ada8424bfeabbc9025d5c7a8","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aded44d1e25cf10f8b8a9aa7c0dffeacbc102642","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"其實唔只supply，有時demand都會有類似的問題。<br />\n例如政府立法提高對盜版軟件的買家的懲罰，對盜版軟件的需求會下降，盜版軟件的均衡價格會下降。咁正版軟件的需求會如何改變？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"盜版軟件既需求量下降 盜版同正版係競爭性需求 正版嘅需求上升 應該係咁？"},{"pid":"3db4591c0205cc86ac538b6178b2e212e9b89b88","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf472514cf77c14ada8424bfeabbc9025d5c7a8","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aded44d1e25cf10f8b8a9aa7c0dffeacbc102642","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"其實唔只supply，有時demand都會有類似的問題。<br />\n例如政府立法提高對盜版軟件的買家的懲罰，對盜版軟件的需求會下降，盜版軟件的均衡價格會下降。咁正版軟件的需求會如何改變？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"盜版軟件既需求量下降 盜版同正版係競爭性需求 正版嘅需求上升 應該係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"教科書通常會用「物品X的價格下降會導致另一種物品的需求減少」作為代替品的定義。<br />\n如果盜版軟件的價格下降，但係正版軟件的需求上升，咁咪好似同上面的定義唔match囉。"},{"pid":"a9d2036444118d66b5c5208602627d537b30ffce","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3db4591c0205cc86ac538b6178b2e212e9b89b88","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf472514cf77c14ada8424bfeabbc9025d5c7a8","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aded44d1e25cf10f8b8a9aa7c0dffeacbc102642","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"其實唔只supply，有時demand都會有類似的問題。<br />\n例如政府立法提高對盜版軟件的買家的懲罰，對盜版軟件的需求會下降，盜版軟件的均衡價格會下降。咁正版軟件的需求會如何改變？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"盜版軟件既需求量下降 盜版同正版係競爭性需求 正版嘅需求上升 應該係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"教科書通常會用「物品X的價格下降會導致另一種物品的需求減少」作為代替品的定義。<br />\n如果盜版軟件的價格下降，但係正版軟件的需求上升，咁咪好似同上面的定義唔match囉。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"但係你講嗰個係物品X價格下降 <span class=\"red\">需求量上升</span> 先會導致物品Y的需求減少<br />\n但而家係盜版需求下降 繼而引致盜版嘅價格下降 <span class=\"red\">盜版嘅需求量都下降</span> 所以正版嘅需求上升 我諗係咁？"},{"pid":"a1d66c6af449551ee524459a3dfa20d7184129e7","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d2036444118d66b5c5208602627d537b30ffce","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3db4591c0205cc86ac538b6178b2e212e9b89b88","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf472514cf77c14ada8424bfeabbc9025d5c7a8","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"盜版軟件既需求量下降 盜版同正版係競爭性需求 正版嘅需求上升 應該係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"教科書通常會用「物品X的價格下降會導致另一種物品的需求減少」作為代替品的定義。<br />\n如果盜版軟件的價格下降，但係正版軟件的需求上升，咁咪好似同上面的定義唔match囉。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"但係你講嗰個係物品X價格下降 <span class=\"red\">需求量上升</span> 先會導致物品Y的需求減少<br />\n但而家係盜版需求下降 繼而引致盜版嘅價格下降 <span class=\"red\">盜版嘅需求量都下降</span> 所以正版嘅需求上升 我諗係咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:04:38.000Z","msg":"樓主的問題都係類似：<br />\n<br />\n教科書教聯合供應(joint supply)嗰陣，通常會寫如果羊肉的價格上升，羊肉的供應量會增加。然後因為殺多咗羊，羊毛的供應就會增加。<br />\n樓主的問題就係：如果因為某啲原因令羊肉的供應減少，羊肉的價格會上升而供應量會減少。咁羊毛的供應應該增加定減少？"},{"pid":"2e0807fd1e975284ebef18cb556a49d4e50e76b8","tid":2263694,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d66c6af449551ee524459a3dfa20d7184129e7","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d2036444118d66b5c5208602627d537b30ffce","tid":2263694,"uid":366694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3db4591c0205cc86ac538b6178b2e212e9b89b88","tid":2263694,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"教科書通常會用「物品X的價格下降會導致另一種物品的需求減少」作為代替品的定義。<br />\n如果盜版軟件的價格下降，